<h2>lorentz: The Lorentz Transform in Relativistic Physics</h2>
<p>The Lorentz transform in special relativity; also the gyrogroup structure of three-velocities.  Includes active and passive transforms and the ability to use units in which the speed of light is not one.  For general relativity, see the
  'schwarzschild' package.</p>
